=head1 HISTORY

The first version of this utility was not bundled with perl package on
FreeBSD.  It was dumber than the current version in several important
areas.  It was faster.

=head1 CREDITS

Thanks to Mathieu Arnold for discussion.

=head1 SEE ALSO

